p;q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3D6%2F8cehJ%2FO8c%26mid%3D24542%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Wireless-Controller-Fallout-Pip-Boy%2F8mzbmmcjzpp1%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fxbox-fallout-pip-boy-controller-is-now-available-to-preorder%2F1100-6536863%2F&amp;event_type=click">Xbox Wireless Controller – Fallout Pip-Boy</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Xbox+Fallout+Pip-Boy+Controller+Is+Now+Available+To+Preorder&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A16&amp;fnarticle_id=6536863&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3D6%2F8cehJ%2FO8c%26mid%3D24542%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Wireless-Controller-Fallout-Pip-Boy%2F8mzbmmcjzpp1%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fxbox-fallout-pip-boy-controller-is-now-available-to-preorder%2F1100-6536863%2F&amp;event_type=click" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/clicks.trx-hub.com\/xid\/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Xbox+Fallout+Pip-Boy+Controller+Is+Now+Available+To+Preorder&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A16&amp;fnarticle_id=6536863&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3D6%2F8cehJ%2FO8c%26mid%3D24542%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Wireless-Controller-Fallout-Pip-Boy%2F8mzbmmcjzpp1%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fxbox-fallout-pip-boy-controller-is-now-available-to-preorder%2F1100-6536863%2F&amp;event_type=click&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Xbox+Fallout+Pip-Boy+Controller+Is+Now+Available+To+Preorder&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A16&amp;fnarticle_id=6536863&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3D6%2F8cehJ%2FO8c%26mid%3D24542%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Wireless-Controller-Fallout-Pip-Boy%2F8mzbmmcjzpp1%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fxbox-fallout-pip-boy-controller-is-now-available-to-preorder%2F1100-6536863%2F&amp;event_type=click">$83 (was $99)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Inspired by Vault-Tec's wearable computer, this controller features a black top case, the outer casing of a Pip-Boy, and a bright green Vault Boy icon in the center. The D-pad sports a healthy radioactive glow, and several other design elements replicate the Valued-Added Targeting System from Fallout. Beyond that, this is a standard Xbox wireless controller.</p><p>It's still the same design that was introduced five years ago, with textured triggers, tactile face buttons, and a very clicky D-pad. These controllers can be powered by AA batteries or a rechargeable battery pack sold separately; they're equipped with an audio jack for wired headphones, and their ergonomic design still makes them very comfortable to use for long stretches. The other great thing about the Xbox controller is that it can be used on multiple platforms, including PC, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and mobile devices via Bluetooth.</p></div>                      </div><p>Xbox gamers looking for a premium option can grab the <a href="https://xboxdesignlab.xbox.com/configure/xbox-elite-wireless-controller-series-2?recipeId=T2NL34G7&amp;FalloutPipBoyPMP_Hero_Elite" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Xbox Elite Series 2 controller</a> with a Fallout finish. Priced at $164.58 (was $185), this premium edition of the controller offers adjustable-tension thumbsticks, shorter hair-trigger locks, rubberized grips, and interchangeable components.</p><p>For more Fallout merchandise, don't miss out on this <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0G4NDX1DX?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" rel="nofollow ">brand-new bundle</a> that celebrates Fallout: New Vegas' 15th Anniversary. Priced at $155, this is a physical re-release of the beloved open-world RPG and it comes with collectible memorabilia.</p><p>You can also catch up on the first season of Fallout through <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Fallout-Season-Amazon-Exclusive-Steelbook/dp/B0F48G8TZ1?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="nofollow ">the limited-edition 4K steelbook</a> that's priced at $40, while the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F7MVP4ZD?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="nofollow ">standard 4K Blu-ray</a> will cost you $30. <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/fallout-season-1-limited-edition-steelbook-restocked-at-amazon/1100-6530906/">You can click this link for more Fallout merchandise</a> like <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D9R9839L?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="nofollow ">action figures</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/MEGA-Building-Collection-Accessories-Collectors/dp/B0D9WNFYWV?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="nofollow ">construction sets</a>, and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DQYFD63T?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="nofollow ">adorable rubber duckies</a>.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/official-nintendo-switch-2-wheel-set-for-mario-kart-gets-first-discount-at-amazon/1100-6536789/">Official Nintendo Switch 2 Wheel Set For Mario Kart Gets First Discount At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/asus-rog-xbox-ally-gets-110-discount-at-amazon/1100-6536577/">Asus ROG Xbox Ally Gets $110 Discount At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/rosalinas-storybook-super-mario-galaxy-dark-horse-nintendo-book-amazon-preorder/1100-6534724/">Super Mario Galaxy Storybook Hardcover Edition Restocked With 15% Discount At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (3)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/psvr-2-horizon-call-of-the-mountain-bundle-is-still-on-sale-for-all-time-best-price/1100-6529777/">PSVR 2 Horizon Call Of The Mountain Bundle Is Still On Sale For All-Time Best Price</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/new-lord-of-the-rings-the-hobbit-illustrated-box-set-restocked-with-nearly-50-discount-at-amazon/1100-6536300/">New Lord Of The Rings &amp; The Hobbit Illustrated Box Set Is Back In Stock With $72 Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/walmart-exclusive-dualsense-icon-blue-controller-is-back-in-stock-for-64/1100-6535294/">Walmart-Exclusive DualSense Icon Blue Controller Is Back In Stock For $64</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
